Constant Field Values

DEFAULT

public static String DEFAULT
The view where annotations are placed by default. This is equivalent to the default view named "_InitialView" and is repeated here only for convenience. For more information on the "_InitialView" please see: http://incubator.apache.org/uima/downloads/releaseDocs/2.2.2-incubating/docs/html/tools/tools.html#ugr.tools.cde.capabilities.sofa_name_mapping
